                            <decoNote type="initial">Pennaflúraðir upphafsstafir bl. <locus from="1v" to="1v">1v</locus> (G), <locus from="6v" to="6v">6v</locus> (M), <locus from="9r" to="9r">9r</locus> (O), <locus from="11v" to="11v">11v</locus> (Þ), <locus from="12r" to="12r">12r</locus> (M, L, H, V, V, H, Þ, O, J), <locus from="13r" to="13r">13r</locus> (Þ), <locus from="15v" to="15v">15v</locus>
                                (Þ), <locus from="16r" to="16r">16r</locus> (T), <locus from="16v" to="16v">16v</locus> (H), <locus from="18r" to="18r">18r</locus>
                                (E), <locus from="22v" to="22v">22v</locus> (H), <locus from="23v" to="23v">23v</locus> (G, G, O), <locus from="24r" to="24r">24r</locus> (H), <locus from="25v" to="25v">25v</locus>
                                (A).</decoNote>
                            <decoNote type="frieze" subtype="secondary">Lítill skrautbekkur með
                                    <q>Anno</q> fyrir framan og ártalið <q>1835</q> fyrir aftan á
